data.description: Spacious and modern, this home boasts an open floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, complemented by a separate one-bedroom, one-bathroom casita. The interior features sleek concrete floors and the kitchen is adorned with stylish two-tone cabinets and quartz countertops. With expansive windows, residents can enjoy breathtaking mountain views. Situated on a generous 1.2-acre lot, this property offers both elegance and practicality, creating a comfortable and inviting living space.
